DESCRIPTION:Go behind the scenes with MAP's conservation team to explore textile preservation in museums. This hands-on workshop covers museum storage and methods\, plus practical tips for safeguarding your cherished textile heirlooms at home.\nAfterward\, join our International Museum Day open house at the conservation lab.\nPlease note that this workshop has limited seats. Registrations are first-come\, first-served.
DTEND:20260524T073000Z
DTSTART:20260524T053000Z
SUMMARY:Caring for Textile Collections
UID:1276@map-india.org
URL:https://map-india.org/map-events/caring-for-textile-collections/
END:VEVENT
