DESCRIPTION:Dive deeper into our collection with a guided walk of our visual storage by Tanya Maheshwari from the MAP Collections team\, and witness the sheer volume of art and artefacts carefully preserved.\n\nIn this session\, visitors will also understand the challenges of storage\, the importance of conservation\, and the surprising discoveries that await within our hidden spaces in the museum.
DTEND:20260524T113000Z
DTSTART:20260524T110000Z
