DESCRIPTION:View the museum with new eyes as you make your way through various exhibitions with a sketchbook in hand. You don’t need to be a professional to join\, we’ll have a briefing at the start to guide you through this drawing session.\n\nAll you need is an open mind and:\n\n-Sketchbook or A4 paper\n\n-Pencil (wood or mechanical) and eraser\n\n-Gel pens or fine liners for outlining\n\n-Colour brush pens\, sketch pens\, or colour pencils (no wet media)\n\n&nbsp\;
